// test/sema/width/struct_cast_expr.test — struct-cast expression
// width fixture (T024 rollover; specs/006-m3-sema/tasks.md Phase 4a).
// Asserts the `StructCastExpr` for `(T)(x).m` carries a Type suffix
// per `emit-ast-format.contract.md` Invariant 2 — the result type
// is the struct field's type after the cast.

// RUN: printf 'module m {\n  wire x;\n  reg q = (T)(x).m;\n}\n' > %t.nsl
// RUN: %nslc -emit=ast %t.nsl | FileCheck %s

// CHECK: (RegDecl {{.*}}name=q
// CHECK: (StructCastExpr
